Steps for create a review for a specific course  (Using Transaction & Rollback)

-> find a course by unique identifier (slug)
-> if the course exist
    -> then create a review with the course id and review payload
    -> otherwise throw an error
-> After create a review get the total review count (review) of a specific course by (movie._id)
-> Then update the course entity (totalRatings:totalReview Count)
-> Return the Review


*** Total Reviews for a specific course would be the total ratings of that course ***
